resonance of 4480 eV appears twice in Table 3.
Temporary, res.pars.of 5478 to 5742 keV have been put
in proper order of energy-sequence. 2 values of res.
par. at 4480 keV seem to be implied that a p-wave re-
sonance stands over a broad s-wave resonance.  However
clarification is requested from the author,78/12
The compiler`s note was confirmed.  And there are 2
